  <brief_title>Study to Assess the Incidence of Intussusception in Children &lt; 2 Years of Age in Singapore</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective, Hospital-based, Multicentre Study to Assess the Incidence of Intussusception in Children &lt; 2 Years of Age in Singapore</official_title>
